licone-based spray lubricant are both good options that will work during both hot and cold seasons.";i:59;s:35:"Genie Garage door opener lubricant.";i:60;s:107:"Specifically for the winter months be sure to use the cold weather screwdrive lubricant Low temp lubricant.";i:61;s:182:"This is recommended for Genie screw drive garage door openers made prior to 2010 such as Excelerator H8000 ISD995 ISD1000 Medallion Series Legacy models H6000 H4000 IMS1000 and more.";i:62;s:55:"We recommend lubricating your garage door twice a year.";i:63;s:111:"This simple lubrication by the homeowner can greatly extend the life of the garage door and garage door opener.";i:64;s:87:"A detailed and extensive service and tune up of your garage door is recommended yearly.";i:65;s:90:"To have this done call Covenant Garage Doors at 770-720-7828 or visit our web site at www.";i:66;s:67:"How and Where to Lubricate a Garage Door to Stop Squeaks - YouTube.";}}